<header>
      <div class="container">
          <div class="intro-text">
              <div class="intro-lead-in">Welcome to Tasking</div>
              <div class="intro-heading">A tool to track projects and send reports</div>
              <%= link_to 'Sign Up', new_user_registration_path, class:"btn btn-xl" %>
          </div>
      </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Services -->
  <section id="services">
      <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
              <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                  <h2 class="section-heading">How it works</h2>
                  <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">Tracking a project and sending progress reports to your clients is now easy</h3>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row text-center">
              <div class="col-md-4">
                  <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
                      <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x circle-background"></i>
                      <i class="fa fa-pencil fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                  </span>
                  <h4 class="service-heading">Plan</h4>
                  <p class="text-muted">Add a project and tasks, listing how long it will take to complete each of them. On your profile, you can state how many hours a day you plan to work. Link the project to your client.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
                  <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
                      <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x circle-background"></i>
                      <i class="fa fa-laptop fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                  </span>
                  <h4 class="service-heading">Work</h4>
                  <p class="text-muted">When you start working on a task, click "Start Task" on the project dashboard. When you take a break on that task or are stuck, you can pause the work on that task and start work on another.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
                  <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
                      <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x circle-background"></i>
                      <i class="fa fa-envelope fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                  </span>
                  <h4 class="service-heading">Report</h4>
                  <p class="text-muted">At the end of each day, you can see your daily report, listing how long you worked on each of your tasks. The report will show you if you are going to finish the project on the estimated date. You can email this report to your client, so they know daily where you stand.</p>
              </div>
          </div>
      </div>
  </section>
